title: 33 more persons test positive for virus in T.N.

content: Tamil Nadu reported 33 cases of COVID-19 on Wednesday, taking the total number of cases to 1,629 (including three who died two who were counted in other States and one person who tested negative after death). The day also saw 27 patients being discharged from… [+1964 chars]
